blish\">Publish your story</a><a class=\"btn-outline px-5 py-3 rounded-sm text-sm\" href=\"/about\">Read the mission</a></div></div></section><section class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 py-12\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-8 flex-wrap gap-4\"><h2 class=\"editorial-h text-2xl font-bold\">The feed</h2><div class=\"flex gap-2 text-xs font-semibold\"><button class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border bg-ink text-paper border-ink\">All</button><button class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-wire text-ink-600\">Stories</button><button class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-wire text-ink-600\">Documentaries</button></div></div><p class=\"text-ink-400 text-sm\">Loading the feed…</p></section></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"border-t border-wire mt-24\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 py-12 grid gap-10 sm:grid-cols-3\"><div><p class=\"editorial-h text-xl font-extrabold\">OPINION<span class=\"text-signal\">PLUS</span></p><p class=\"text-sm text-ink-400 mt-2 max-w-xs\">A platform where every person gets a masthead — their name, their logo, their truth, at the top of the page.</p></div><div><p class=\"wire-tag mb-3\">Read</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-signal\" href=\"/\">Feed</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-signal\" href=\"/about\">About OpinionPlus</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"wire-tag mb-3\">Legal &amp; support</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-signal\" href=\"/privacy\">Privacy policy</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-signal\" href=\"/contact\">Contact us</a></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"rule\"><p class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 py-5 text-xs text-ink-400\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> OpinionPlus. Every byline belongs to the person who wrote it.</p></div></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-05173f67f96f24be.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragm